  "texts": [
    "Importantly, considering the potential future legal ramifications for researchers, more ethical practice could manifest by monitoring and publicly disclosing the use and development of AI datasets and tools as proposed by European Commission, EU-DGRI (2024).",
    "The adult entertainment industry is afflicted by similar problems, and concerns are amplified because of the widespread accessibility of mature content by minors and the treatment of women in the work place (Gilkerson 2021; Stokes 2012).",
    "Notably, 96% of deepfakes are sexually explicit depictions of non-consenting women (Tenbarge 2023).",
    "Furthermore there are profound implications of child pornography (Olson 2021).",
    "Kirchengast (2020) reviews current regulatory mechanisms and legislative powers in the US, concluding that present solutions require thorough critique and serious investigation."
  ]
}